      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable commuter for someone who understands it has some years on it. While the engine starts up reliably and the transmission shifts through all gears, there is some noticeable oil dampness underneath and the suspension is beginning to feel a bit loose over bumps. The exterior has its share of minor dings, scratches, and some clear coat fading on the roof, while the interior shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpets. It is a solid, honest car that performs its basic duties but will likely require some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future.",
