    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Drive away with confidence in this well-maintained gem! This vehicle is in good condition, offering a smooth and reliable ride that's perfect for your next chapter. It has been cared for and shows just minor, expected signs of use, making it a fantastic value for anyone seeking a dependable and stylish car. Ready for many more miles of memories!",
