    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector-grade example that looks and drives as if it just left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like finish with no scratches, chips, or dents to be found. Inside, the interior is pristine; the leather is supple, the dashboard is crack-free, and every electronic component functions perfectly, showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, it is in peak condition with a documented service history, offering a driving experience that is as tight and responsive as the day it was manufactured.",
