    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is in really solid shape for its next owner! It drives smoothly, has been well-loved, and is just perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love to find it a great new home!",
