      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This naturally aspirated powerhouse delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The vehicle benefits from documented preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. Equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, the chassis dynamics remain precise and communicative. The exterior and interior reflect a well-maintained driver\u2019s car with minor patina consistent with its age, offering a visceral analog experience for the discerning petrolhead.",
      "price": 34500.0,
