      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and is ready for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep shine, though it shows minor, typical road wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, and all electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound; the engine pulls strong, the transmission shifts smoothly, and I have kept a detailed log of all scheduled maintenance, including a recent brake service and fluid flush. It\u2019s a reliable, comfortable drive that looks as good as it performs. Clean title in hand.",
